Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Starlight! Ready\Nto celebrate your first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearth's Warming Eve\Nhere in Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking I\Nmight just skip it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Derpy is Best Pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:02:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\Nby YayPonies\Nhttp://yayponies.eu/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.49,0:02:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,SKIP HEARTH'S WARMING EVE?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just find it all\Na little silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mostly a day dedicated to\Npresents and candy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.14,0:02:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And why would you deny\Nyourself presents and candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I THINK what Spike\Nmeans to say is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearth's Warming is about\Nmore than presents and candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a time to spend\Nwith friends and family
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,when we celebrate a\Nvery important day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in Equestria's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I think to most ponies,\Nit's just an excuse
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,for silly songs and fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,not a day to remember\Nsome old story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you just haven't\Nheard the right
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearth's Warming\NEve story yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth ponies, pegasi\Nand unicorns sing songs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,around a hearth to fight\Nback an eternal winter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,caused by the\Nmythical Windigos?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Every foal and fill\Nknows that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Not THAT one. My\Nfavorite holiday story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hearth's Warming Tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooooo! I love that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the story of a powerful\Nunicorn named Snowfall Frost
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,who hated Hearth's\NWarming Eve!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It all began many moons\Nago in Canterlot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Every home in Canterlot was\Nfilled with Holiday spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Every home except one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was said of Snowfall that\Nshe was almost as studied
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,as Starswirl the Bearded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost, since everypony knows\Nthat Starswirl was an expert
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,at everything from\Ntransfiguration,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dimensional Calibration,\NTeleportation--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We get it.\NStarswirl's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:04:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. The point is, Snowfall\Nwas also a powerful unicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted to be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that got in the way\Nof that was a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that batch is\Nruined. SNOWDASH!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Snowdash was Snowfall's\Nloyal assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get this mess cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Those foolish ponies were\Nringing those blasted bells
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,outside the window and\NI lost my concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. Ponies\Nactually enjoying
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearth's Warming Eve. Where\Ndid they get that crazy idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is nothing\Nto celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearth's Warming\NEve is a menace,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,a dangerous day for\Nall of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous? It's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the day we remember\Nhow unicorns, pegasi,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and earth ponies came\Ntogether in friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to defeat the Windigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That silly legend\Nis the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Telling everypony that\Nsinging songs and being nice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,will solve anything? I've\Nspent years studying magic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's not how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you might be\Nmissing the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Work hard, learn and use your\Nskills to better Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT'S a worthy\Ngoal for anypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But by all means, if you\Nwant to go home early,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,ignore all of the work you\Nhave and spend the rest --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,SWEET!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I HATE Hearth's Warming Eve!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All of Equestria\Nwould be better off
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,if we just skipped\Nthe day all together.
