Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the spell is cast, all of\NEquestria will be better off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And they'll have\Nme to thank for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Snowfall doesn't like\NHearth's Warming Eve
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so she decides to cast a spell\Nto get rid of it all together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems a little extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Says the pony who tried\Nto make everypony the same
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,by replacing their cutie\Nmarks with equal signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I THINK what Spike is trying\Nto say is that everypony
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,has their reasons for doing\Nthings. Even Snowfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I could\Ncontinue the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we might just find\Nout what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Snowfall was all set to cast\Nher spell that would erase
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearth's Warming\NEve for all time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,when a voice from the hearth\Ncaught her attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You SURE you wanna\Ngo through with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Spirit of Hearth's\NWarmin' Past, that's who.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And you and me have got\Nto have us a little chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A spirit! I didn't cast any\Nspirit-summoning spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think a spell\Nlike that would get by
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,without some powerful\Nforces noticing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got our attention,\NSnowfall Frost
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've got some\Npretty strong opinions
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,on this spell of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be along in a bit.\NFor now it's just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get a move on.\NWe got a ton to see
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and barely any time\Nto see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a spell to cast. And\NI don't need a history lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,about Hearth's Warming Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't goin' to the past\Nto learn about the holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We're goin' to\Nlearn about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ As a young thing,{\i0}\N{\i1} life sure is something ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You go makin' choices{\i0}\N{\i1} large and small ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Always growing{\i0}\N{\i1} like a seedling ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ and playin' is{\i0}\N{\i1} like dreaming ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And before you know{\i0}\N{\i1} it big and tall. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And every little{\i0}\N{\i1} bitty choice you make ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Sends you down a path{\i0}\N{\i1} to who you are today ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ So let's take a little{\i0}\N{\i1} trip down memory lane ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And see just what{\i0}\N{\i1} the past has to say. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Awww, look how\Ncute you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're\Nnot too upset it's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearth's Warming Eve, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The seeds of the past,{\i0}\N{\i1} they grow pretty fast ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Just look at who{\i0}\N{\i1} you were back then ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The seeds as they grow,{\i0}\N{\i1} look what they can show ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Reveal the truth{\i0}\N{\i1} time and again ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what do you think\Nyou are doing, Snowfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Decorating the classroom\Nfor Hearth's Warming Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Flintheart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to learn\Nto be a powerful unicorn,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,did you not?\NI do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the way that one\Nbecomes a powerful unicorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Work hard, learn\Nand use your skills
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to better Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do these help\Nyou to learn magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be strong enough to\Nstop Windigos and help ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just a story\Nwe tell little ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Real magic takes\Ntime to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Spend your time learning to\Nbecome a powerful unicorn,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,or play with your toys and\Nmake nothing of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Then some distress,{\i0}\N{\i1} words so careless ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Standing there, you{\i0}\N{\i1} don't know what to do ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling helpless,\Ncan't make it hurt less
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ So you go and change{\i0}\N{\i1} your point of view. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And in that moment{\i0}\N{\i1} though you didn't know it ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Your defenses set up{\i0}\N{\i1} walls you built to last ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Leading to the pony{\i0}\N{\i1} you've become today ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And the spell you're{\i0}\N{\i1} about to cast, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ it all comes from your past. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The seeds of the past'{\i0}\N{\i1} we grow up so fast ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Some hurts never go away ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The seeds as they grow,{\i0}\N{\i1} this we can't let go ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ All tied to this one holiday ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit?\NWhat am I supposed to--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,SNOWFALL FROST! IT IS I,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,THE SPIRIT OF HEARTH'S\NWARMING PRESENTS!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, don't you mean\Npresent, like, the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Toys, Hearth's Warming\Ndolls. Here! Want a cupcake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Presents. All of\Nthe pointless things
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that ponies waste\Ntheir time on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Snowfall. It's not what\Nthe gift is that matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it's what the gift MEANS!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean anything.\NIt's just stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! Sometimes a\Ncupcake means I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Or a toy means Hi!\NHow ya doin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes a book means,\N"Your mane looks AMAZING!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes a scarf means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,well, a scarf usually\Nmeans you look cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand\Nanything you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My Spirit of Hearth's Warming\NPresents-sense is going off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That means a song\Nis coming on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Take a look at everything ♪{\i0}\N{\i1} ♪ around you ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ All the smells that{\i0}\N{\i1} surely will astound you ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Open up your heart;{\i0}\N{\i1} it will surround you ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ In the magic of{\i0}\N{\i1} Hearth's Warming Eve ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The little things{\i0}\N{\i1} that make it better ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Little ponies{\i0}\N{\i1} spreading cheer! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Give a toy, a hug, a sweater ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Memories that last all year! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The present's always{\i0}\N{\i1} filled with presents ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Large, medium and small ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Sometimes the most{\i0}\N{\i1} important things ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Aren't very big at all. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ What a party! There's{\i0}\N{\i1} so much to see here! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I can't believe you{\i0}\N{\i1} didn't want to be here ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ You would've had a{\i0}\N{\i1} blast I guarantee here ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ THIS is the spirit of{\i0}\N{\i1} Hearth's Warming Eve! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The cider's flowing,{\i0}\N{\i1} this is living! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Come on and feel the beat! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Life is better{\i0}\N{\i1} when you're givin' ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Each time you do{\i0}\N{\i1} it feels so sweet! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The present's always{\i0}\N{\i1} filled with presents ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ So come on open your eyes ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Spend time with{\i0}\N{\i1} ponies just like you ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ and watch your spirits rise ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The present's always{\i0}\N{\i1} filled with presents ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Take a look around ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The reason for the holiday ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ is quite easily found ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Yes the reason for the{\i0}\N{\i1}holiday is quite easily found ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And the reason is to{\i0}\N{\i1} be with your friends! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And the reason is to{\i0}\N{\i1} be with your friends! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you're doing your\NPinkie Pie voice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happens next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the party was--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,WAIT! Can we take\Na quick break?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to refill my cocoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But hurry up! We're\Nalmost to the best part!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The party was in full swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Snowdash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, whatever is\Nthe matter, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it the eggnog?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I put in too\Nmuch cinnamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! The eggnog was\Nawesome, Flutterholly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just mad at somepony\Nwho was complaining
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,about how awful\NHearth's Warming Eve is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose that pony's\Nname starts with "Snow"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:15:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And ends with "frost"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She said Hearth's Warming Eve\Nis just an excuse to party
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'd all be better\Noff spending time working
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to make Equestria\Na better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What does Snowfall think a\Nbetter Equestria looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And using their abilities for\Nthe benefit of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we've got\Neverything on Snowfall's list
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think a perfect\NEquestria looks a lot like
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a Hearth's Warming Eve party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too. Too bad it's going\Nto be the last one EVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever...ever...ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit? What do you mean?\NWhat's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the Spirit of Hearth's\NWarming Yet to Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here to show me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what future Hearth's\NWarming Eves are like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No. For there are no more\NHearth's Warming Eves
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for me to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You will succeed in erasing\Nthe holiday as you wished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I see a cold wind{\i0}\N{\i1} blowing through ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I see days neither{\i0}\N{\i1} fun nor free ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I see a future{\i0}\N{\i1} caused by you ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I see a path not{\i0}\N{\i1} meant to be ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The future should{\i0}\N{\i1} be filled with magic ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ dreams and wishes{\i0}\N{\i1} brought to life ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But the days ahead{\i0}\N{\i1} are dark and tragic ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ no time for hope{\i0}\N{\i1} when all is strife ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Whatever might have been ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ all the dreams{\i0}\N{\i1} that ponies share ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Because of you,{\i0}\N{\i1} Snowfall Frost ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Now the future is{\i0}\N{\i1} a cold nightmare ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,WINDIGOS!? They\Naren't real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a little\Nfilly's story!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They are all too\Nreal, Snowfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And your actions will\Nallow them to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The future of Equestria\Nshall be bathed in a blanket
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of eternal snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I never meant for this to\Nhappen. I didn't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see how important\NHearth's Warming Eve was!
