Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's it. Thanks for\Nletting me read you the story.
